{"type":"message","id":"ea781f6b","parentId":"ef26052e","timestamp":"2026-05-12T11:49:41.905Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full details. Let me summarize the two models clearly for Jo.\n","thinkingSignature":"3e76e5e05ba8aeb59c0a27f8adbd711d65ff2e8715683208e44ccb3fe9f41c7c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n📊 Ray 模型矩陣解析：\n\n---\n\n## 🤖 ray-v1（1.5B）\n| 項目 | 規格 |\n|------|------|\n| 參數量 | **1.5B** |\n| 模型架構 | Qwen2 |\n| 量化 | Q4_K_M（壓縮版） |\n| Context | 32,768 tokens |\n| Embedding | 1,536 |\n| 用途 | 快速策略提案、即時訊號解析 |\n\n**系統 Prompt：**\n> \"You are Ray, Jo's dedicated quantitative trading agent.\"\n\n**個性：高速、執行導向、適合每日掃描**\n\n---\n\n## 🧠 ray-deep-v1（7B）\n| 項目 | 規格 |\n|------|------|\n| 參數量 | **7.6B** |\n| 模型架構 | Qwen2 |\n| 量化 | Q4_K_M |\n| Context | 32,768 tokens |\n| Embedding | 3,584（更豐富的語意空間）|\n| GPU | 1（7B 需要 GPU 加速）|\n| 用途 | 深度歸因、策略進化、情緒分析 |\n\n**系統 Prompt：**\n> \"You are Ray-Deep (Qwen 7B), the Chief Strategist of the Tina Quant System.\"\n\n**個性：深度推理、複雜分析、策略進化**\n\n---\n\n## 協作分工\n\n```\n每日掃描 / 快速信號  → ray-v1（1.5B，< 3 秒）\n策略回測 / 深度報告  → ray-deep-v1（7B，< 15 秒）\n緊急技術分析         → ray-v3（qwen3.5:4b）\n```\n\n目前的下載佇列：`qwen2.5:3b`（還在跑）完成後會加入陣容。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":376,"output":410,"cacheRead":31616,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32402,"cost":{"input":0.00011279999999999999,"output":0.0004919999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0018969599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0025017599999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778586572406,"responseId":"065246cd90e3319a6366f8e00ec2f1ba"}}
