{"type":"message","id":"5f9df341","parentId":"82ec5eab","timestamp":"2026-05-12T11:52:40.339Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a massive codebase. Let me now analyze the key scripts to understand LLM usage patterns and network dependency. Let me look at the most important ones first.\n\nKey areas to analyze:\n1. **本地 LLM 使用**：哪些腳本調用 Ollama（ray-v1, ray-deep-v1, qwen2.5:7b 等）\n2. **網路獲取數據**：yfinance, finmind, twse api, 等\n3. **MiniMax 使用**：哪些腳本用 MiniMax API\n4. **K線/報價更新**：哪些腳本獲取實時報價\n\n\n5. **連網學習**：ray_web_learner, ray_econ_learner 等\n\nI'll start examining the critical files to map out these patterns—checking the LOCAL_CONFIG for routing rules, reviewing the main brain files and momentum scanners to understand LLM dependencies, and looking at the web learning components to see how they handle network data.\n","thinkingSignature":"273f8d360f92d08a17a1a56cc45b4fb83b9fc92d081b2ccadc1462bc1881cd75"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n數量太多，我分段掃描。先看關鍵腳本：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vmmqacwceumx_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nimport re, os\n\n# Scan key scripts for LLM and network patterns\nfiles = {\n    'LOCAL_CONFIG.md': r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\LOCAL_CONFIG.md',\n    'ray_brain.py': r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_brain.py',\n    'ray_nl2code.py': r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_nl2code.py',\n    'us_momentum.py': r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\us_momentum.py',\n    'us_scan_live.py': r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\us_scan_live.py',\n    'ray_data_center.py': r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_data_center.py',\n    'ray_engine.py': r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_engine.py',\n    'ray_integrated_brain.py': r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_integrated_brain.py',\n    'ray_minimax_cloud.py': r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_minimax_cloud.py',\n    'ray_web_learner.py': r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_web_learner.py',\n    'ray_econ_learner.py': r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_econ_learner.py',\n    'update_quotes.py': r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\update_quotes.py',\n    'us_entry.py': r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\us_entry.py',\n    'daily_premarket.py': r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\daily_premarket.py',\n}\n\nfor name, path in files.items():\n    if os.path.exists(path):\n        with open(path, 'r', encoding='utf-8', errors='ignore') as f:\n            content = f.read()\n        llm_ollama = bool(re.search(r'ollama|ray-v1|ray-deep|qwen.*api|/api/chat', content, re.I))\n        llm_minimax = bool(re.search(r'minimax|api-key|Remnant', content, re.I))\n        net_yfinance = bool(re.search(r'yfinance|yf\\.|yahoo', content, re.I))\n        net_finmind = bool(re.search(r'finmind|twse|fugle', content, re.I))\n        net_http = bool(re.search(r'requests\\.|urllib|http\\.client|aiohttp|httpx', content))\n        print(f'{name}: LLM_Ollama={llm_ollama}, LLM_Minimax={llm_minimax}, Net_yfinance={net_yfinance}, Net_Finmind={net_finmind}, HTTP={net_http}')\n\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":19474,"output":895,"cacheRead":43648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64017,"cost":{"input":0.0058422,"output":0.0010739999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0026188799999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.009535079999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778586743427,"responseId":"06524779f5543cbf2cfa3c12c087733f"}}
