{"type":"message","id":"fc572730","parentId":"2f2eb056","timestamp":"2026-05-12T12:00:38.322Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All 5 steps are done. Let me summarize what was done.\n","thinkingSignature":"949b912e5a476f8566c591a8ddeab3d3bb8df55ccb3e50c39f96aa46524465d4"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n✅ **改善方案完成！** `qwen2.5:3b` 已安裝成功。\n\n---\n\n## 📋 執行摘要\n\n### ✅ Step 1：`llm_router.py` — 統一路由層（新建）\n- 建立 `LLMRouter` 類，四層分流：\n  - `Layer 1` → ray-v1（本地，< 3s）\n  - `Layer 2` → MiniMax（雲端，3-15s）\n  - `Layer 3` → MiniMax + web（連網學習）\n- 便捷函式：`fast()` / `deep()` / `web()`\n\n### ✅ Step 2：`ray_brain.py` — 接入 Router\n- `fast_propose()` 走 `ROUTER.fast()` → Layer 1\n- `deep_analysis()` 走 `ROUTER.deep()` → Layer 2（MiniMax）\n- 保留降級：Router 失敗 → 直接 Ollama fallback\n\n### ✅ Step 3：`ray_integrated_brain.py` — 接入 Router\n- `LLMAdvisor.ask()` 增加 `layer` 參數\n- `propose_signal()` 預設 Layer 2（MiniMax）\n- 深度分析走 MiniMax，而非本地 7B\n\n### ✅ Step 4：`ray_web_learner.py` / `ray_econ_learner.py` — 改走 MiniMax\n- `validate_with_7b()` → `ROUTER.deep()` → MiniMax\n- `batch_summarize()` → `ROUTER.deep()` → MiniMax\n\n### ✅ Step 5：`LOCAL_CONFIG.md` — 更新路由規則\n- 清晰分層原則文檔化\n- 數據獲取（yfinance/finmind）永遠不走 LLM\n\n---\n\n## 🔑 核心改變\n\n| 之前 | 之後 |\n|------|------|\n| 複雜分析直接 call Ollama 7B（易超時/幻覺）| 複雜分析走 MiniMax |\n| 連網學習走本地 Qwen（無 web 能力）| 連網學習走 MiniMax + web |\n| 無統一路由，混用嚴重 | 所有 LLM 調用經過 Router |\n| `us_momentum.py` / `us_scan_live.py` 已✅（保持）| 技術指標純本地計算 |\n\n`qwen2.5:3b`（1.9 GB）已就緒，可作為備用快速模型。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":210,"output":542,"cacheRead":81664,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82416,"cost":{"input":0.000063,"output":0.0006504,"cacheRead":0.00489984,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00561324}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778587218368,"responseId":"06524955af6d1787480bb5f2ab261fd4"}}
