{"type":"message","id":"3ae051cd","parentId":"a713764b","timestamp":"2026-05-12T12:09:18.955Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All done! Let me summarize the execution results.\n","thinkingSignature":"10e2f317541f46e07832328ddf470f3f593560815fe8af3a4bdc6cf870a3e7dd"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n✅ **全部執行完成！** 語法驗證：9/9 ✅\n\n---\n\n## 📋 執行摘要\n\n### P0：ray_self_correct.py + tina_daily_self_correct.py ✅\n- 雙層架構維持，但底層置換：\n  - Layer 1 → `ROUTER.fast()` → **ray-v1 本地**\n  - Layer 2 → `ROUTER.deep()` → **MiniMax 雲端**（不再走 Ollama 7B）\n- 保留 `_ollama_fallback()` 降級函式\n\n### P1：ray_cloud_brain.py ✅\n- Tavily 搜尋結果 → `ROUTER.web()` → **MiniMax Layer 3**\n- 風控審核 → `ROUTER.deep()` → **MiniMax Layer 2**\n- 不再走 Ollama ray-v1/ray-deep-v1\n\n### P2：news_sentiment.py ✅\n- 升級：關鍵詞匹配 → `ROUTER.web()` → **MiniMax Layer 3**\n- 保留關鍵詞作為 fallback\n- 輸出同時包含 LLM 分析結果 + 關鍵詞對照\n\n### P3：llm_router.py 增強 ✅\n- 新增備用模型映射：\n  - Layer 1: `ray-v1` → `qwen2.5:3b` → `qwen3.5:4b`\n  - Layer 2: `ray-deep-v1` → `qwen2.5:7b`\n- 新增 `status()` 顯示完整模型鏈\n\n---\n\n## 🏗️ 現在的 Router 狀態\n\n```\nLayer 1（< 3s）：ray-v1 → qwen2.5:3b → qwen3.5:4b\nLayer 2（3-15s）：MiniMax → ray-deep-v1 → qwen2.5:7b\nLayer 3（連網）：MiniMax + web fetch\n```\n\n**已整合腳本（9個）：** ray_brain, ray_integrated_brain, ray_web_learner, ray_econ_learner, ray_self_correct, tina_daily_self_correct, ray_cloud_brain, news_sentiment + llm_router.py 本身"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":215,"output":492,"cacheRead":112384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113091,"cost":{"input":0.0000645,"output":0.0005903999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00674304,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0073979399999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778587747060,"responseId":"06524b650181916d35f5108942d16091"}}
