2 13:31:16,284 [INFO] Step 2: 關鍵詞過濾...\r\n2026-05-12 13:31:16,284 [INFO]   過濾後 0 筆（關聯內容）\r\n2026-05-12 13:31:16,284 [INFO] Step 3: Math Gate 檢查...\r\n2026-05-12 13:31:16,284 [INFO]   Gate 通過 0 筆\r\n2026-05-12 13:31:16,284 [INFO] Step 4: 7B 審核...\r\n2026-05-12 13:31:16,284 [INFO] === Ray Web Learner 完成 ===\r\n2026-05-12 13:31:16,287 [INFO]   總 web_source 記錄: 0\r\n2026-05-12 13:37:45,849 [INFO] === Ray Web Learner 啟動 ===\r\n2026-05-12 13:37:47,436 [INFO] 抓取 0 筆\r\n2026-05-12 13:37:47,437 [INFO] 過濾後 0 筆\r\n2026-05-12 13:37:47,437 [INFO] Gate通過 0 筆\r\n2026-05-12 13:37:47,438 [INFO] 總 web_source: 0\r\n===\r\n2026-05-12 13:44:28,272 [INFO] === Ray Econ Learner 啟動 ===\r\n2026-05-12 13:44:28,272 [INFO] Step 1: Jina Reader 抓取...\r\n2026-05-12 13:44:28,629 [WARNING] Jina Reader failed: HTTP Error 403: Forbidden\r\n2026-05-12 13:44:28,829 [WARNING] Jina Reader failed: HTTP Error 403: Forbidden\r\n2026-05-12 13:44:28,829 [INFO]   抓取並通過預選: 0 篇\r\n2026-05-12 13:44:28,830 [INFO] Step 2: 去重複檢查...\r\n2026-05-12 13:44:28,830 [INFO]   去重後: 0 篇\r\n2026-05-12 13:44:28,830 [INFO] Step 3: 7B 批量摘要...\r\n2026-05-12 13:44:28,830 [INFO]   產生 0 條規則\r\n2026-05-12 13:44:28,833 [INFO] === 完成。WEB_SOURCE 總計: 1 筆 ===","cwd":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778588094305}}
{"type":"message","id":"e99df523","parentId":"be3ffa59","timestamp":"2026-05-12T12:15:36.674Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have enough data. Let me analyze the log issues and propose improvements.\n\n## Issues Found\n\n### 1. Encoding issue - ray_data_center.log shows garbled Chinese\nThe log was written with the wrong encoding (likely cp950 / Big5 instead of UTF-8). The `[INFO] === Ray Data Center 啟動 ===` appeared as `??` etc. The content itself is correct but when displayed without UTF-8, it becomes garbled.\n\nRoot cause: `sys.stdout.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8', errors='replace')` is set in scripts but `logging.FileHandler` might not inherit the encoding.\n\n### 2. ray_web_learner.log - \"feedparser not available\"\nThe script tries to use `feedparser` but it's not installed. Falls back to \"manual mode\" and returns 0 items. This means the web learner isn't actually learning anything.\n\n### 3. ray_econ_learner.log - \"Jina Reader failed: HTTP Error 403: Forbidden\"\nJina Reader is blocked (403 Forbidden). The script then has 0 articles to process, and the 7B batch summarize gets 0 rules.\n\n\nThe backtest log is generating excessive error output—97KB of \"possibly delisted\" warnings when testing 676 symbols (210 succeeded, 466 failed). This creates noise that drowns out actual backtest results. Additionally, the web learner isn't discovering new insights since feedparser isn't available, and econ learner isn't processing anything due to Jina being blocked by 403 errors.\n","thinkingSignature":"0e4537cb108387e34addda54d73af99c72446fcf0d1744f299b971cfe702ced8"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n慢思考完整檢討：\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 PowerShell 日誌檢討\n\n### 📊 日誌現況\n\n| 日誌檔 | 大小 | 問題 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| `ray_backtest_630.log` | **97 KB** | 💥 flood：466 次 delisted 錯誤 |\n| `ray_data_center.log` | 2 KB | 🟡 編碼錯誤：中文變乱码 |\n| `ray_web_learner.log` | 1 KB | 🔴 空跑：feedparser 無效，0 筆資訊 |\n| `ray_econ_learner.log` | 1 KB | 🔴 空跑：Jina Reader 403 Forbidden |\n\n---\n\n### 🔴 四大核心問題\n\n#### 問題 1：ray_backtest_630.log — **97KB flood 攻擊**\n\n```python\n# 根因：強力掃描 676 個符號，466 個已下市/ETF\n# 每個失敗產生重複的 ERROR 文字（2行 × 466 = 932 行）\n# → 97KB 噪音蓋過有意義的內容\n```\n\n**需要改善：**\n- `EX443`, `EX444`... `EX457` — 這些是已在 NYSE 摘牌的股票\n- 這些不需要報告（無意義）\n- 應該：**安靜跳過，只報告真正重要的錯誤**\n\n#### 問題 2：ray_data_center.log — **編碼錯誤**\n\n```\n[INFO] === Ray Data Center 啟動 ===  （正常）\n[INFO] Written: VTI 363.63 RSI:58.3  （正常）\n...但是有另一個 session 寫出的內容變成乱码：\n?? / ?? / ??\n```\n\n**根因：** `sys.stdout.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8')` 只影響 `print()`，但 `logging.FileHandler` 使用系統預設編碼（Big5/cp950）。\n\n**需要改善：**\n```python\n# logging 要明確指定 encoding='utf-8'\nhandler = logging.FileHandler(filename, encoding='utf-8')\nformatter = logging.Formatter('%(asctime)s [%(levelname)s] %(message)s')\nhandler.setFormatter(formatter)\n```\n\n#### 問題 3：ray_web_learner.log — **feedparser 無效，整個學習模組空跑**\n\n```\n[WARNING] feedparser not available, using manual mode\n抓取 0 筆 → 過濾後 0 筆 → Gate通過 0 筆 → 7B審核 0 筆\n```\n\n**根因：** `feedparser` 套件未安裝。整個 web learner 沒有資料來源。\n\n**需要改善：**\n- 安裝 `feedparser`：`pip install feedparser`\n- 或替換為其他 RSS source（如 Yahoo Finance RSS）\n- 或使用 MiniMax Tavily 替代（已經在 ray_cloud_brain.py 用了）\n\n#### 問題 4：ray_econ_learner.log — **Jina Reader 403 Forbidden，0 筆處理**\n\n```\n[WARNING] Jina Reader failed: HTTP Error 403: Forbidden\n抓取並通過預選: 0 篇 → 去重後: 0 篇 → 產生 0 條規則\n```\n\n**根因：** Jina Reader API 被拒絕（403），幾乎不可能成功。\n\n**需要改善：**\n- Jina Reader 已不可靠，應替換為 Tavily（已在 ray_cloud_brain.py 使用）\n- 或使用 MiniMax 原生 web fetch（Layer 3）\n\n---\n\n### 🟡 改善方案\n\n#### 【立即】修復 ray_backtest_630.py 的 ERROR flood\n\n```python\n# 在 yfinance 失敗時，不要打 ERROR，只打 DEBUG\n# 只對真正重要的錯誤打 WARNING/ERROR\n\n# 現況（太多噪音）：\nlogging.error(f\"['{sym}']: possibly delisted; no timezone found\")\n\n# 改善（安靜跳過已下市符號）：\nif \"possibly delisted\" in str(e):\n    logging.debug(f\"[{sym}] delisted, skip\")\nelse:\n    logging.warning(f\"[{sym}] failed: {e}\")\n```\n\n#### 【立即】修復 logging 編碼\n\n```python\n# 在每個腳本的 logging.init 裡：\nimport logging, codecs\n\nlog_file = \"logs/ray_xxx.log\"\nhandler = logging.FileHandler(log_file, encoding='utf-8')\nformatter = logging.Formatter('%(asctime)s [%(levelname)s] %(message)s')\nhandler.setFormatter(formatter)\n_log = logging.getLogger(\"ray_xxx\")\n_log.addHandler(handler)\n_log.setLevel(logging.INFO)\n```\n\n#### 【中期】ray_web_learner.py 修復 feedparser\n\n```bash\npip install feedparser\n```\n\n或修改為不依賴 feedparser，使用 Tavily 作為主要資訊源。\n\n#### 【中期】ray_econ_learner.py 修復 Jina Reader\n\n廢除 Jina Reader，全部改走 Router Layer 3（MiniMax web fetch）。\n\n---\n\n### 📋 優先順序\n\n| 優先 | 項目 | 效益 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **P0** | ray_backtest_630.py 抑制 delisted flood | 日誌從 97KB → < 5KB |\n| **P1** | logging 全面加 `encoding='utf-8'` | 解決中文乱码 |\n| **P2** | ray_web_learner.py 安裝 feedparser 或改 Tavily | 恢复 Web 學習 |\n| **P3** | ray_econ_learner.py 廢除 Jina Reader | 恢复 Econ 學習 |\n\n---\n\n要立即執行嗎？建議從 **P0（ray_backtest_630.py ERROR flood）** 開始。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":884,"output":1561,"cacheRead":116544,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118989,"cost":{"input":0.0002652,"output":0.0018732,"cacheRead":0.00699264,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00913104}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778588094308,"responseId":"06524cbff266d41e72787d4b159a1973"}}
