{"type":"message","id":"eace04db","parentId":"b3f290f0","timestamp":"2026-05-12T12:23:50.271Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_s21iftoaauhr_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Total logging/print calls: 24\r\n  ...LOG_DIR.mkdir(exist_ok=True)\r\n\r\nlogging.basicConfig(\r\n    filename=str(LOG_DIR / \"r...\r\n  ...backtest_630.log\"),\r\n    level=logging.INFO,\r\n    format=\"%(asctime)s [%(levelname...\r\n  ...name)s] %(message)s\"\r\n)\r\n_log = logging.getLogger(\"backtest_630\")\r\n\r\nprint(\"=== Ray ...\r\n  ...ng.getLogger(\"backtest_630\")\r\n\r\nprint(\"=== Ray 630 檔回測系統 ===\")\r\nprint(f\"目標: S&P 500...\r\n  ...rint(\"=== Ray 630 檔回測系統 ===\")\r\nprint(f\"目標: S&P 500 + Nasdaq 100 + SOX 30\")\r\nprint(...\r\n  ...P 500 + Nasdaq 100 + SOX 30\")\r\nprint()\r\n\r\n# =======================================...\r\n  ...tickers.update(sp500)\r\n        print(f\"S&P 500: {len(sp500)} 檔\")\r\n    except Excep...\r\n  ...xcept Exception as e:\r\n        print(f\"S&P 500 抓取失敗，使用備用 ({len(SP500_TICKERS)} 檔)...\r\n  ...l_tickers.update(ndx)\r\n        print(f\"新增 Nasdaq 100: {len(ndx)} 檔\")\r\n    except E...\r\n  ...xcept Exception as e:\r\n        print(f\"NDX 抓取失敗，使用備用 ({len(NDX_TICKERS)} 檔)\")\r\n   ..."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":170,"aggregated":"Total logging/print calls: 24\r\n  ...LOG_DIR.mkdir(exist_ok=True)\r\n\r\nlogging.basicConfig(\r\n    filename=str(LOG_DIR / \"r...\r\n  ...backtest_630.log\"),\r\n    level=logging.INFO,\r\n    format=\"%(asctime)s [%(levelname...\r\n  ...name)s] %(message)s\"\r\n)\r\n_log = logging.getLogger(\"backtest_630\")\r\n\r\nprint(\"=== Ray ...\r\n  ...ng.getLogger(\"backtest_630\")\r\n\r\nprint(\"=== Ray 630 檔回測系統 ===\")\r\nprint(f\"目標: S&P 500...\r\n  ...rint(\"=== Ray 630 檔回測系統 ===\")\r\nprint(f\"目標: S&P 500 + Nasdaq 100 + SOX 30\")\r\nprint(...\r\n  ...P 500 + Nasdaq 100 + SOX 30\")\r\nprint()\r\n\r\n# =======================================...\r\n  ...tickers.update(sp500)\r\n        print(f\"S&P 500: {len(sp500)} 檔\")\r\n    except Excep...\r\n  ...xcept Exception as e:\r\n        print(f\"S&P 500 抓取失敗，使用備用 ({len(SP500_TICKERS)} 檔)...\r\n  ...l_tickers.update(ndx)\r\n        print(f\"新增 Nasdaq 100: {len(ndx)} 檔\")\r\n    except E...\r\n  ...xcept Exception as e:\r\n        print(f\"NDX 抓取失敗，使用備用 ({len(NDX_TICKERS)} 檔)\")\r\n   ...","cwd":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778588630271}}
{"type":"message","id":"d2104e28","parentId":"eace04db","timestamp":"2026-05-12T12:24:01.874Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So `ray_backtest_630.py` actually doesn't have ERROR level logging for delisted stocks. It silently skips them (the `else: skipped += 1` branch). But the log file still shows those ERROR messages - which means they're coming from yfinance itself (which uses logging internally).\n\nThe problem is `logging.basicConfig` with `level=logging.INFO` means INFO and above are logged. yfinance internally logs `ERROR` messages for delisted stocks. These propagate through the Python logging system.\n\nThe fix:\n1. Change `logging.basicConfig(level=logging.INFO)` to `level=logging.WARNING` — so ERROR from yfinance won't be logged\n\n\n2. Or silence yfinance's logger specifically by setting it to a higher threshold, keeping INFO for the backtest's own messages while blocking yfinance's ERROR spam\n\nNow I need to check if the other scripts like `ray_data_center.log` have the same encoding issue with their logging setup.\n","thinkingSignature":"00eb94cf1840fc10d44e858c812a9125655e2a96e5a2da5621c9d0d6bdf82f65"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7q0231nget1m_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nimport re\n\nfiles = {\n    'ray_data_center.py': r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_data_center.py',\n    'ray_web_learner.py': r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_web_learner.py',\n    'ray_econ_learner.py': r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_econ_learner.py',\n    'ray_backtest_630.py': r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_backtest_630.py',\n}\n\nfor name, path in files.items():\n    c = open(path, encoding='utf-8', errors='ignore').read()\n    # Find logging.FileHandler or basicConfig\n    handlers = re.findall(r'FileHandler\\([^)]+\\)|basicConfig\\([^)]+\\)', c)\n    levels = re.findall(r'level=logging\\.\\w+', c)\n    encodings = re.findall(r'encoding=[^\\)\\,]+', c)\n    print(f'{name}:')\n    print(f'  Handlers: {handlers}')\n    print(f'  Levels: {levels}')\n    print(f'  Encodings: {encodings}')\n    print()\n\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":566,"output":501,"cacheRead":127744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128811,"cost":{"input":0.00016979999999999998,"output":0.0006012,"cacheRead":0.0076646399999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00843564}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778588630274,"responseId":"06524ed82b75996a2ae5648d6531d143"}}
