{"type":"message","id":"0057e3e0","parentId":"47819b19","timestamp":"2026-05-12T12:25:55.049Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The yfinance logger propagates to root, and root level is 30 (WARNING). So yfinance DEBUG/INFO messages wouldn't show at root level WARNING.\n\nBut the log showed ERRORs. These must come from yfinance setting its own logger level or from stderr of yfinance itself.\n\nActually - the log file shows `yfinance` ERRORs but the script only uses `_log` (backtest_630 logger) and `logging.basicConfig`. The `logging.basicConfig` only sets up the root logger for file output. But yfinance also outputs to stderr via its own handlers.\n\nWait - but the `logging.basicConfig` writes to `ray_backtest_630.log`. So how did the yfinance ERRORs get into that file?\n \nSo `logging.basicConfig` with a filename parameter only attaches a FileHandler to the root logger, and yfinance ERRORs would propagate up to root and get written to that file. Since root is at WARNING level, those ERRORs would definitely be captured, and the actual ERROR messages in the log show yfinance trying to fetch symbols like EX443 through EX457.\n\nThe script itself only logs two things to that file: the startup message and the completion summary. So those yfinance ERROR lines must be coming from yfinance's own logging calls, which means yfinance is logging errors directly about failed ticker fetches. The script's direct logging only captures the startup and completion messages, so those ERROR lines are coming from yfinance's internal logging when requests fail. This means I need to reduce the verbosity at the yfinance logger level itself, not just in the script's logging configuration.\n","thinkingSignature":"b3187f1862f315c9e7be474e15f6883d865de4b386ff350124e29e2da52aeb1d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lay7kwtj8fuh_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nimport re\nc = open(r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_backtest_630.py', encoding='utf-8', errors='ignore').read()\n# Look for where logging is configured + yfinance is imported\nprint('Full file beginning (first 120 lines):')\nlines = c.split(chr(10))\nfor i, l in enumerate(lines[:120]):\n    print(f'{i+1}: {l}')\n\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":169,"output":464,"cacheRead":130112,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130745,"cost":{"input":0.0000507,"output":0.0005568,"cacheRead":0.00780672,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00841422}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778588737919,"responseId":"06524f438aba8c01ad626013bad51faf"}}
{"type":"message","id":"939e0b91","parentId":"0057e3e0","timestamp":"2026-05-12T12:25:55.238Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_lay7kwtj8fuh_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Full file beginning (first 120 lines):\r\n1: # -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\r\n2: \"\"\"\r\n3: ray_backtest_630.py\r\n4: 擴展回測到 630 檔：S&P 500 + Nasdaq 100 + SOX 30\r\n5: \"\"\"\r\n6: import sys, sqlite3, json, time, logging\r\n7: from pathlib import Path\r\n8: sys.stdout.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8', errors='replace')\r\n9: \r\n10: import yfinance as yf\r\n11: import numpy as np\r\n12: import pandas as pd\r\n13: from concurrent.futures import ThreadPoolExecutor, as_completed\r\n14: \r\n15: DB = 'ray_wisdom.db'\r\n16: LOG_DIR = Path(\"logs\")\r\n17: LOG_DIR.mkdir(exist_ok=True)\r\n18: \r\n19: logging.basicConfig(\r\n20:     filename=str(LOG_DIR / \"ray_backtest_630.log\"),\r\n21:     level=logging.INFO,\r\n22:     format=\"%(asctime)s [%(levelname)s] %(message)s\"\r\n23: )\r\n24: _log = logging.getLogger(\"backtest_630\")\r\n25: \r\n26: print(\"=== Ray 630 檔回測系統 ===\")\r\n27: print(f\"目標: S&P 500 + Nasdaq 100 + SOX 30\")\r\n28: print()\r\n29: \r\n30: # ============================================================\r\n31: # 1. 主要指數\r\n32: # ============================================================\r\n33: INDICES = {\r\n34:     \"SPX\": (\"^GSPC\", \"S&P 500\"),\r\n35:     \"NDX\": (\"^NDX\", \"Nasdaq 100\"),\r\n36:     \"SOX\": (\"^SOX\", \"Philadelphia Semiconductor\"),\r\n37: }\r\n38: \r\n39: # ============================================================\r\n40: # 2. S&P 500 成分股（常見大型股）\r\n41: # ============================================================\r\n42: SP500_TICKERS = [\r\n43:     \"AAPL\", \"MSFT\", \"GOOGL\", \"AMZN\", \"NVDA\", \"META\", \"TSLA\", \"BRK-B\", \"UNH\", \"JNJ\",\r\n44:     \"V\", \"XOM\", \"JPM\", \"PG\", \"MA\", \"HD\", \"CVX\", \"LLY\", \"ABBV\", \"MRK\",\r\n45:     \"PEP\", \"KO\", \"COST\", \"AVGO\", \"WMT\", \"MCD\", \"TMO\",