{"type":"message","id":"38c8586e","parentId":"a464d1fe","timestamp":"2026-05-12T12:36:11.611Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a comprehensive picture of the web learning state. Let me compile a thorough review.\n\nKey findings:\n1. **WEB_SOURCE count: 1** — After all the web learning scripts, only 1 actual web-sourced wisdom exists in the DB\n2. **wisdom_corrections total: 63** — Most are from `batch_corrected` (fix1_batch_correct.py), not from web learning\n3. **wisdom_logs: 360 total** — Only 1 passed, 172 failed, ~187 unprocessed\n4. **The 62 non-WEB_SOURCE corrections** are almost all `batch_corrected` corrections to VEA/BND/SPY/etc strategies, NOT external web knowledge\n\n\n5. The web learning pipeline is essentially non-functional: feedparser returned zero entries, Jina hit a 403 error, and despite all the LLM integration work with Router, Tavily, and MiniMax, we're not actually capturing external web knowledge into the system.\n","thinkingSignature":"857511a4821660f4b655e550181d7ddcd8b2f1a76c8059d0599a89e25c795c6d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n慢思考完整檢討連網學習進度：\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 連網學習現況（2026-05-12）\n\n### 📊 資料庫現況\n\n| 項目 | 數量 | 備註 |\n|------|------|------|\n| wisdom_corrections 總數 | **63** | |\n| WEB_SOURCE（真正外部學習）| **1 筆** | ❌ 極少 |\n| wisdom_logs 總數 | **360** | |\n| wisdom_logs passed | **1** | ❌ |\n| wisdom_logs failed | **172** | |\n| 未處理 | **~187** | |\n\n---\n\n### 🔴 核心問題：連網學習幾乎完全失效\n\n**1筆 WEB_SOURCE 來自「手動 demo」，不是系統自動學習。**\n\n看看 `batch_corrected` 修正的內容（62筆非 WEB_SOURCE）：\n```\nVEA: \"The fast EMA (9) is too close to slow EMA (21)\"  → conf=0.0\nBND: \"The entry condition threshold is set to zero\"  → conf=0.80\nSPY: 低 Sharpe Ratio, possibly due to overfitting  → conf=0.0\n```\n**這些是回測修正，不是外部連網學習。**\n\n---\n\n### 🔍 各模組問題\n\n| 模組 | 之前 | 之後 | 現況 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| **ray_web_learner.py** | RSS: 0筆 | Tavily: 未測試 | ❌ 從未成功抓取過 |\n| **ray_econ_learner.py** | Jina 403 | Tavily: 未測試 | ❌ 從未成功抓取過 |\n| **feedparser** | 0 entries（Yahoo已失效）| 已安裝但Yahoo RSS已失效 | ❌ |\n| **Router Layer 3** | 不存在 | ✅ 已整合 | 待驗證 |\n| **Tavily** | 未使用 | ✅ 已在 ray_cloud_brain | 待測試 |\n\n---\n\n### 🟡 根本原因分析\n\n```\nray_web_learner.py 的流程：\n  RSS (0筆) → 過濾 (0筆) → Gate (0筆) → validate (0次) → 寫入 0 筆\n\nray_econ_learner.py 的流程：\n  Jina Reader → 403 Forbidden → 0篇 → batch_summarize → 0條規則\n  \n即使 Router 已經整合好 Tavily，也沒有真正被調用！\n```\n\n---\n\n### 📋 改善方案\n\n#### 【P0】立即執行：測試 Tavily 實際可用性\n\n```python\n# 測試 Tavily 是否正常\nimport requests\nresp = requests.post(\n    \"https://api.tavily.com/search\",\n    json={\"query\": \"quantitative trading Sharpe ratio\", \"api_key\": TAVILY_KEY, \"max_results\": 5},\n    timeout=15\n)\nprint(resp.json())\n```\n\n#### 【P1】ray_web_learner.py 主程式替換為 Tavily\n\n目前 `daily_web_learning()` 已經改成先抓 Tavily，但**從未實際執行過**。\n\n#### 【P2】ray_econ_learner.py 主程式替換為 Tavily\n\n`fetch_tavily_articles()` 已寫入，但 `econ_web_learning()` 主循環**仍然在用舊的 Jina 邏輯**。\n\n#### 【P3】實際執行並驗證寫入 DB\n\n---\n\n要立即測試 Tavily 並修正嗎？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":795,"output":966,"cacheRead":148864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":150625,"cost":{"input":0.0002385,"output":0.0011592,"cacheRead":0.00893184,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01032954}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778589340106,"responseId":"0652519da6f07487760cab654103f325"}}
