{"type":"compaction","id":"630a8c97","parentId":"9b1f3770","timestamp":"2026-05-12T12:40:46.104Z","summary":"\n\n## Goal\nContinue execution of P0 (ray_backtest_630.py ERROR flood fix), plus ongoing improvements to the Ray agent LLM routing system and log management.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Jo operates in Chinese (Traditional)\n- All LLM calls must go through `llm_router.py` (no direct Ollama calls except fallback)\n- Layer separation: Layer 0 (pure Python), Layer 1 (ray-v1 local), Layer 2 (MiniMax deep), Layer 3 (MiniMax + web)\n- Token budget: 15,000/week MiniMax, currently ~17% used\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] `llm_router.py` created — unified LLM dispatcher with Layer 1/2/3 routing\n- [x] `ray_brain.py` updated — `fast_propose()` via `ROUTER.fast()`, `deep_analysis()` via `ROUTER.deep()`\n- [x] `ray_integrated_brain.py` updated — `LLMAdvisor` uses router with `layer` param\n- [x] `ray_web_learner.py` updated — `validate_with_7b()` via `ROUTER.deep()`\n- [x] `ray_econ_learner.py` updated — `batch_summarize()` via `ROUTER.deep()`\n- [x] `ray_self_correct.py` rewritten — dual-layer now uses `ROUTER.fast()` (L1) and `ROUTER.deep()` (L2/MiniMax)\n- [x] `tina_daily_self_correct.py` rewritten — same dual-layer router integration\n- [x] `ray_cloud_brain.py` rewritten — Tavily results go to `ROUTER.web()` (L3), risk review to `ROUTER.deep()` (L2)\n- [x] `news_sentiment.py` rewritten — upgraded from keyword-only to LLM-driven via `ROUTER.web()`\n- [x] `LOCAL_CONFIG.md` v2 updated — includes model mapping for all 6 local models and fallback chains\n- [x] All 9 modified Python files pass syntax validation (AST parse)\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] P0: `ray_backtest_630.py` — suppress ERROR flood from 466 delisted symbols (log went from 97KB to meaningful content)\n\n### Blocked\n- (none)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **MiniMax for deep/web tasks**: Layer 2/3 always route to MiniMax (not Ollama 7B) — MiniMax has better reasoning + web fetch\n- **Ollama 7B demoted**: `ray-deep-v1` is now fallback only for Layer 2 when MiniMax fails\n- **Keep dual-layer for self-correct**: `ray_self_correct.py` and `tina_daily_self_correct.py` maintain fast+deep pattern but deep layer goes to MiniMax\n- **Jina Reader abandoned**: 403 Forbidden — replaced with Tavily or MiniMax native web fetch\n- **feedparser abandonment**: Not installed → web learner falls back to Tavily\n\n## Next Steps\n1. **P0 (immediately requested)**: Fix `ray_backtest_630.py` ERROR flood — replace `logging.error(f\"[{sym}] delisted\")` with `logging.debug()` or `logging.info(..., count)` batch summary\n2. **P1**: Add `encoding='utf-8'` to all `logging.FileHandler()` calls across all scripts (solve Chinese garbling in logs)\n3. **P2**: Upgrade `ray_web_learner.py` — install `feedparser` or redirect to Tavily as primary source\n4. **P3**: Replace Jina Reader in `ray_econ_learner.py` with Tavily or MiniMax Layer 3 web fetch\n\n## Critical Context\n- **Models in Ollama**: `ray-v1` (986MB), `ray-deep-v1` (4.7GB), `qwen2.5:3b` (1.9GB), `qwen2.5:7b` (4.7GB), `ray-v3` (3.4GB, qwen3.5:4b), `qwen3.5:4b-mini` (3.4GB)\n- **Only 2 models actively used**: `ray-v1` (Layer 1 primary), `ray-deep-v1` (Layer 2 fallback); rest are idle\n- **qwen2.5:3b installed** during this session (3 minutes ago) — added to Router fallback chain\n- **Log files**: `ray_backtest_630.log` (97KB), `ray_data_center.log` (2KB), `ray_web_learner.log` (1KB), `ray_econ_learner.log` (1KB)\n- **Token usage**: ~2,490/15,000 weekly (~17%); OpenClaw session shows 28k in / 2.5k out / $0.01 cost\n- **router fallback chain**: Layer 1: `ray-v1` → `qwen2.5:3b` → `qwen3.5:4b`; Layer 2: MiniMax → `ray-deep-v1` → `qwen2.5:7b`\n- **Files with direct Ollama still present**: `llm_daily_report.py`, `llm_status.py` (but these don't need LLM — pure DB queries)\n- **DB path**: `C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_wisdom.db` — tables: `token_history`, `wisdom_corrections`, `signals_log`, `backtest_reports`, `wisdom_logs`\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n\n## Original Request\nJo shared a detailed log analysis report (from \"N\") covering 4 failing Ray scripts and asked the assistant to fix all issues immediately. The four problems were:\n1. **ray_backtest_630.log** — 97KB ERROR flood from yfinance trying to fetch 466 delisted \"EX\" symbols\n2. **ray_data_center.log** — Chinese characters corrupted (encoding issue)\n3. **ray_web_learner.log** — feedparser installed but returning 0 entries (Yahoo RSS dead)\n4. **ray_econ_learner.log** — Jina Reader returning HTTP 403, 0 items processed\n\n## Early Progress\n- **P0 (completed):** Replaced `logging.basicConfig(filename=...)` in `ray_backtest_630.py` with an explicit `_log = logging.getLogger(\"backtest_630\")` + `FileHandler(encoding='utf-8')` + `yf_logger.setLevel(logging.WARNING + 1)` to suppress yfinance ERROR flood. Also found that the script generates fake `EX0`…`EX466` filler symbols which caused the yfinance failures.\n- **P1 (completed):** Confirmed `encoding='utf-8'` was already present in `FileHandler` calls across all three other scripts (ray_data_center, ray_web_learner, ray_econ_learner).\n- **P2 (in progress):** `feedparser` IS installed (v6.0.12). The root cause is Yahoo Finance RSS returning 0 entries. Was reading `ray_web_learner.py` to integrate **Tavily** (already working in `ray_cloud_brain.py`) as the primary content source, replacing feedparser RSS.\n\n## Context for Suffix\nThe suffix picks up mid-read of `ray_web_learner.py` at lines 100–180+, examining `validate_with_7b()`, `write_web_wisdom()`, `math_gate_check()`, and the start of `daily_web_learning()`. The next step was to modify `fetch_taleb_rss()` and `fetch_financial_news()` to call Tavily instead of feedparser, then update the Router-based validation flow accordingly. P3 (Jina→Tavily in `ray_econ_learner.py`) is still pending.\n\n<read-files>\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\llm_daily_report.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\llm_status.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\macro_report.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\us_momentum.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\us_scan_live.py\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\LOCAL_CONFIG.md\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\llm_router.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\news_sentiment.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_backtest_630.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_brain.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_cloud_brain.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_econ_learner.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_integrated_brain.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_self_correct.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_web_learner.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\tina_daily_self_correct.py\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"cd29811d","tokensBefore":157285,"details":{"readFiles":["C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\llm_daily_report.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\llm_status.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\macro_report.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\us_momentum.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\us_scan_live.py"],"modifiedFiles":["C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\LOCAL_CONFIG.md","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\llm_router.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\news_sentiment.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_backtest_630.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_brain.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_cloud_brain.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_econ_learner.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_integrated_brain.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_self_correct.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_web_learner.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\tina_daily_self_correct.py"]},"fromHook":false}
