{"type":"message","id":"7d5afd54","parentId":"64a2f25d","timestamp":"2026-05-12T12:43:53.434Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the 3 WEB_SOURCE records:\n- 148: manual demo (from before)\n- 149: \"當Sharpe比率低于0.5時，表明投資回報相對於風險過低。\" - from batch_summarize\n- 150: \"RSI指標在65至35之間時，表明市場處於超買或超賣狀態。\" - from batch_summarize\n\nThe econ_learner is working. The web_learner's 10 articles all failed the `validate_with_7b()` gate. Let me check why.\n\nActually wait - ray_web_learner's output said \"總 web_source: 3 筆\". \n\nLooking at the execution order, econ_learner ran first and wrote its 3 records, then ray_web_learner ran and saw 10 articles pass the initial filter, but all 10 must have failed the LLM validation gate since the total stayed at 3.\n\nI'm noticing a discrepancy though—the log says \"過濾: 10 筆\" but then also shows \"Gate通過: 10 筆\", which suggests the articles passed both the initial filter and the LLM validation, yet no new records were written to the database.\n\nLet me trace through ray_web_learner's save function to see where the write might be failing, since it's supposed to insert validated articles into wisdom_corrections. I'm noticing a discrepancy in the record counts — if web_learner ran after econ_learner and added 0 records, the total should still be 3, but the output shows \"總 web_source: 3 筆\" which seems to reflect the count before the run. The write or count logic might be off, but this is secondary to confirming the core flow works: Tavily fetches articles, they're validated through the LLM, and they're being saved to the database. Let me move forward with testing ray_web_learner and then run the full learning cycle to verify everything end-to-end.","thinkingSignature":"a1fd3a36bddd8276b92f81beec6cfbe31dc40fc1424b8040bc06ec6b332235a0"},{"type":"text","text":"**econ_learner ✅ 正常** — Tavily 抓 10 篇，寫入 3 條規則（RSI / Sharpe）。\n\nray_web_learner 顯示 10 篇 Gate 通過但總數仍是 3，檢查一下：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jqrzuu6vwmfe_1","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":40,"offset":60,"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_web_learner.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":27875,"output":527,"cacheRead":15749,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44151,"cost":{"input":0.0083625,"output":0.0006324,"cacheRead":0.0009449399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00993984}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778589817146,"responseId":"0652537acd5944692e33dc2aac25bebb"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7afb7ec5","parentId":"7d5afd54","timestamp":"2026-05-12T12:43:53.441Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_jqrzuu6vwmfe_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    \"\"\"Taleb RSS（備用）\"\"\"\n    try:\n        import feedparser\n        insights = []\n        try:\n            f = feedparser.parse(RSS_FEEDS[\"taleb\"])\n            for entry in f.entries[:3]:\n                insights.append({\"title\": entry.title, \"summary\": entry.summary[:200], \"source\": \"Taleb_RSS\"})\n        except Exception as e:\n            _log.warning(f\"Taleb RSS failed: {e}\")\n        return insights\n    except ImportError:\n        return []\n\ndef fetch_financial_news():\n    \"\"\"Yahoo Finance RSS（備用，已不穩）\"\"\"\n    try:\n        import feedparser\n        insights = []\n        try:\n            f = feedparser.parse(RSS_FEEDS[\"yahoo_spy\"])\n            for entry in f.entries[:5]:\n                insights.append({\"title\": entry.title, \"summary\": entry.summary[:200] if hasattr(entry, 'summary') else \"\", \"source\": \"Yahoo_Finance\"})\n        except Exception as e:\n            _log.warning(f\"Yahoo RSS failed: {e}\")\n        return insights\n    except ImportError:\n        return []\n\ndef filter_keywords(text):\n    keywords = [\"sharpe\", \"kelly\", \"fat-tail\", \"volatility\", \"drawdown\", \"momentum\", \"rsi\", \"macd\", \"mean reversion\", \"portfolio\", \"risk management\", \"position sizing\", \"stop loss\", \"tail risk\", \"asymmetric\", \"convexity\", \"black swan\"]\n    text_lower = text.lower()\n    return any(kw in text_lower for kw in keywords)\n\ndef classify_insight(text):\n    text_lower = text.lower()\n    if any(k in text_lower for k in [\"taleb\", \"black swan\", \"fragility\"]):\n        return \"TALEB\"\n    elif any(k in text_lower for k in [\"thorp\", \"kelly\", \"blackjack\"]):\n        return \"THORP\"\n\n[124 more lines in file. Use offset=100 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778589833441}}
{"type":"message","id":"6cd2ba6b","parentId":"7afb7ec5","timestamp":"2026-05-12T12:43:58.114Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see `filter_keywords()` is different from `is_relevant()`. Let me check the `write_web_wisdom()` function which actually writes to the DB.","thinkingSignature":"b5d263d1375290b7ac42292961af66e6525d3e55784b4f4da2f9683500256328"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_awz51gosbuxo_1","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":140,"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_web_learner.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":28833,"output":98,"cacheRead":15749,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44680,"cost":{"input":0.0086499,"output":0.0001176,"cacheRead":0.0009449399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.009712440000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778589833443,"responseId":"0652538a4ef76cb608a76738f7b1e61d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a916ed42","parentId":"6cd2ba6b","timestamp":"2026-05-12T12:43:58.122Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_awz51gosbuxo_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        _log.error(f\"7B validation failed: {e}\")\n        return {\"valid\": False, \"conflict\": \"error\", \"action\": str(e)}\n\ndef write_web_wisdom(insight, validation_result):\n    conn = sqlite3.connect(DB_PATH)\n    c = conn.cursor()\n    insight_text = insight.get(\"title\", \"\") + \" \" + insight.get(\"summary\", \"\")\n    classification = classify_insight(insight_text)\n    confidence = 0.7 if validation_result.get(\"valid\") else 0.4\n\n    c.execute('INSERT INTO wisdom_corrections (axiom_id, symbol, diagnosis, corrected_json, confidence, meta_label, created_at) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)',\n        (0, \"WEB_SOURCE\", f\"[{classification}] {insight.get('title', 'N/A')}\",\n         json.dumps({\"source\": insight.get(\"source\", \"UNKNOWN\"), \"insight\": insight.get(\"summary\", \"\"), \"validation\": validation_result}),\n         confidence, json.dumps({\"source\": \"web_learner\", \"type\": classification}),\n         time.strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")))\n\n    conn.commit()\n    conn.close()\n    _log.info(f\"Web wisdom written: {insight.get('title')[:50]} conf={confidence}\")\n\ndef math_gate_check(insight):\n    text = (insight.get(\"summary\", \"\") + \" \" + insight.get(\"title\", \"\")).lower()\n    for pattern in [\"sharpe < 0\", \"no stop loss\", \"all in\", \"leverage > 10x\"]:\n        if pattern in text:\n            _log.warning(f\"Math Gate rejected: {pattern}\")\n            return False\n    return True\n\ndef daily_web_learning():\n    _log.info(\"=== Ray Web Learner 啟動 ===\")\n    collected = []\n\n    # ── 主要來源：Tavily 搜尋（取代 RSS）───\n    queries = [\n        \"quantitative trading strategy Sharpe ratio\",\n        \"momentum trading RSI mean reversion\",\n        \"risk management position sizing stop loss\",\n        \"portfolio optimization fat-tail black swan\",\n    ]\n    for q in queries:\n        results = fetch_tavily_news(q, max_results=3)\n        collected.extend(results)\n    _log.info(f\"Tavily 抓取 {len(collected)} 筆\")\n\n    # ── 備用：RSS feeds───\n    taleb = fetch_taleb_rss()\n    news = fetch_financial_news()\n    if taleb or news:\n        collected.extend(taleb)\n        collected.extend(news)\n\n[34 more lines in file. Use offset=190 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778589838122}}
{"type":"message","id":"9443e76e","parentId":"a916ed42","timestamp":"2026-05-12T12:44:02.061Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The code looks correct. Let me check the rest of `daily_web_learning()` to see the logic that decides whether to call `write_web_wisdom()`.","thinkingSignature":"4675cc710368d749d4047538cda7f4f38efff9095533cadfc255de96dcf4e546"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_k1vcl3ny1nnv_1","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":35,"offset":190,"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_web_learner.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":29511,"output":98,"cacheRead":15749,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45358,"cost":{"input":0.0088533,"output":0.0001176,"cacheRead":0.0009449399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00991584}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778589838124,"responseId":"0652538f15ebf8b39489dd7b01e681e0"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ca5b8698","parentId":"9443e76e","timestamp":"2026-05-12T12:44:02.068Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_k1vcl3ny1nnv_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        _log.info(f\"RSS 備用 {len(taleb)+len(news)} 筆（已穩定）\")\n\n    total = len(collected)\n    _log.info(f\"抓取 {total} 筆\")\n\n    filtered = [i for i in collected if filter_keywords(i.get(\"title\", \"\") + i.get(\"summary\", \"\"))]\n    _log.info(f\"過濾後 {len(filtered)} 筆\")\n\n    gate_passed = [i for i in filtered if math_gate_check(i)]\n    _log.info(f\"Gate通過 {len(gate_passed)} 筆\")\n\n    for insight in gate_passed[:5]:\n        validation = validate_with_7b(insight.get(\"title\", \"\") + \" \" + insight.get(\"summary\", \"\"))\n        if validation.get(\"valid\"):\n            write_web_wisdom(insight, validation)\n            _log.info(f\"  OK: {insight.get('title')[:50]}\")\n\n    conn = sqlite3.connect(DB_PATH)\n    c = conn.cursor()\n    c.execute(\"SELECT COUNT(*) FROM wisdom_corrections WHERE symbol='WEB_SOURCE'\")\n    web_count = c.fetchone()[0]\n    conn.close()\n    _log.info(f\"總 web_source: {web_count}\")\n\n    return {\"collected\": len(collected), \"filtered\": len(filtered), \"gate_passed\": len(gate_passed), \"total_web_wisdom\": web_count}\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    result = daily_web_learning()\n    print(f\"\\n=== 連網學習結果 ===\")\n    print(f\"抓取: {result['collected']} 筆\")\n    print(f\"過濾: {result['filtered']} 筆\")\n    print(f\"Gate通過: {result['gate_passed']} 筆\")\n    print(f\"總 web_source: {result['total_web_wisdom']} 筆\")\n    print(\"\\n連網學習模組就緒\")"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778589842068}}
{"type":"message","id":"15884b34","parentId":"ca5b8698","timestamp":"2026-05-12T12:44:14.133Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the flow:\n1. `collected` from Tavily (let's say 12)\n2. `filtered` by keywords (10)\n3. `gate_passed` by math gate (10)\n4. For each of the first 5 gate_passed, call `validate_with_7b()`\n5. If valid, write to DB\n\nThe output said:\n- \"抓取: 12 筆\"\n- \"過濾: 10 筆\"  \n- \"Gate通過: 10 筆\"\n- \"總 web_source: 3 筆\"\n\nSo `validate_with_7b()` was called for up to 5 articles, and none passed validation. \n\nThe LLM validation layer is too strict—all 5 candidates got rejected. But if the earlier run with 10 articles produced 3 rules through `batch_summarize`, those should have written to the DB. Yet the current count is only 3 total, and this run added 0, which means either the earlier run didn't actually write those rules, or something's off with how the database is being queried.\n\nLet me trace through the actual execution order more carefully to see what really happened.","thinkingSignature":"f1396f7669e9e86a77fcb7fb74e8531d6e2fdb794e1942e50fce39b7a6f05e9a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ilbn2pgkfaef_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"import sqlite3; conn=sqlite3.connect(r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_wisdom.db'); c=conn.cursor(); c.execute('SELECT id,created_at,diagnosis,confidence FROM wisdom_corrections WHERE symbol=? ORDER BY id',('WEB_SOURCE',)); rows=c.fetchall(); print('Total WEB_SOURCE:',len(rows)); [print(r) for r in rows]; conn.close()\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":30041,"output":371,"cacheRead":15749,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46161,"cost":{"input":0.009012299999999999,"output":0.0004452,"cacheRead":0.0009449399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.010402439999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778589842069,"responseId":"06525393c3ce75f8307822bd24f17d5f"}}
