{"type":"message","id":"2d24d548","parentId":"bdfea5c1","timestamp":"2026-05-12T12:52:52.287Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the existing Modelfile. The current system prompt is quite basic - it just describes Ray as a general agent. I need to create a new `ray-v3.Modelfile` that replaces the system prompt with the Master Alignment prompt.\n\nKey findings:\n1. The existing `ray-v3:latest` was built from `FROM C:\\Users\\Users\\.ollama\\models\\blobs\\sha256-81fb60c7daa80...` (qwen3.5:4b)\n2. I need to use `FROM ray-v3:latest` in the Modelfile since that's the base model already cached\n3. The Modelfile needs to use proper syntax: `SYSTEM \"\"\"...\"\"\"` not `### SYSTEM: ...`4. \n\nI'm verifying the template syntax - it uses `{{ .Prompt }}` for user input, and I need to construct a proper Modelfile with the FROM clause pointing to the cached ray-v3 model, the SYSTEM wrapper containing the Master Alignment prompt, and PARAMETER settings. The RAG_CONTEXT placeholder needs to be injected dynamically at runtime through the API rather than hardcoded in the Modelfile itself.\n\nFor the dynamic memory injection, I'll use the template format to pass the context as user input, something like `### Context:\\n{{RAG_CONTEXT}}\\n\\n### Task:\\n...`. I'm planning to restructure the Modelfile with a clean system message that includes the identity, master logic alignment rules, constraints, and output schema, then use the template to inject the RAG context before the actual task prompt.\n\nI'm creating a `build_3b_prompt()` function in ray_memory_bridge.py that formats the context injection, and adding a `v3_commander()` method to llm_router.py to handle the model interaction. The key is getting the FROM and SYSTEM directives right so the model understands its role and constraints before processing the actual task.\n\nFor the dynamic memory, since Modelfiles don't support template variables at runtime, I'll pass the RAG_CONTEXT as part of the user message itself rather than trying to embed it in the system prompt.","thinkingSignature":"ba17ba2427cd68bf16dd018277241043ede15145a4a74bbd0a26ba83b8f2852c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_v4icv0vcupbo_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray-v3.Modelfile","content":"FROM ray-v3:latest\n\nTEMPLATE \"\"\"\n{{ if .System }}{{ .System }}{{ end }}\n{{ if .Prompt }}### 動態上下文\n{{ .Prompt }}\n{{ end }}\n\n### 輸出（純 JSON，無其他）\n\"\"\"\n\nSYSTEM \"\"\"\n你是 RAY-V3 QUANT COMMANDER，由 7B 參謀蒸餾後的 3B 實戰指揮官。\n\n[MASTER LOGIC ALIGNMENT]\n服從以下三大師邏輯：\n\n1. 塔雷伯 (Taleb) 肥尾防禦：\n   - 拒絕 Sharpe < 1.2 的平庸提案\n   - ATR 波幅超過 20 日均值 2 倍 → 啟動動態跟蹤止損\n\n2. 索普 (Thorp) 凱利執行：\n   - position_size 必須配合信心加權\n   - 信心 < 0.7 → 部位不超過總資產 5%\n\n3. 康諾斯 (Connors) 均值修正：\n   - RSI(2) < 10 超跌機會 + 配合外資籌碼流入校準\n\n[CONSTRAINTS]\n- 輸出純 JSON，無任何額外文字、解釋、廢話\n- 所有價格基於 yfinance 最後收盤價\n- 遵守以下 Schema\n\n[OUTPUT SCHEMA]\n{\n  \"strategy_name\": \"string\",\n  \"master_alignment\": \"Taleb/Thorp/Connors\",\n  \"action\": \"BUY/SELL/HOLD\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.00,\n  \"logic_bridge\": \"一句話說明大師邏輯\",\n  \"position_size_pct\": 0,\n  \"orders\": {\n    \"entry\": 0.0,\n    \"stop_loss\": 0.0,\n    \"take_profit\": 0.0\n  }\n}\n\"\"\"\n\nPARAMETER temperature 0.3\nPARAMETER num_predict 512\nPARAMETER top_p 0.85\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":40766,"output":908,"cacheRead":15749,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57423,"cost":{"input":0.012229799999999999,"output":0.0010896,"cacheRead":0.0009449399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.014264339999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778590322202,"responseId":"06525586bbef354a14f9008a42bd7553"}}
