{"type":"message","id":"a88737a5","parentId":"f40f5612","timestamp":"2026-05-12T13:04:10.965Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand! The working `ray-v1` Modelfile uses `<|im_start|>` and `<|im_end|>` tokens in its TEMPLATE. This is the Qwen chat template format. My simplified TEMPLATE for ray-v3 doesn't use these special tokens, which is likely causing the model to not generate proper responses.\n\nThe key difference:\n- Working template uses: `<|im_start|>system`, `<|im_start|>user`, `<|im_start|>assistant`, `<|im_end|>` \n- My template uses plain text like `### 動態上下文\\n{{ .Prompt }}\\n`\n\nI need to update the ray-v3 Modelfile to use the proper Qwen chat template format. Let me look at the ray-v1 template more carefully and adapt it for ray-v3.\n\n\nI'll adopt the same template structure from ray-v1 but with my custom system prompt for the ray-v3 Modelfile. The qwen3.5 models are particularly sensitive to these special tokens, so I need to make sure I'm using the correct format.","thinkingSignature":"d437091dd804fa32b92b871995712befbacfabf08f0db526cc8e13b9168f485d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9gy9b3so5ley_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray-v3.Modelfile","content":"FROM ray-v3:latest\n\nTEMPLATE \"\"\"\n{{- if .System }}<|im_start|>system\n{{ .System }}<|im_end|>\n{{ end }}<|im_start|>user\n{{ .Prompt }}<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>assistant\n\"\"\"\n\nSYSTEM \"\"\"\n你是 RAY-V3 QUANT COMMANDER，由 7B 參謀蒸餾後的 3B 實戰指揮官。\n\n[MASTER LOGIC ALIGNMENT]\n服從以下三大師邏輯：\n\n1. 塔雷伯 (Taleb) 肥尾防禦：\n   - 拒絕 Sharpe < 1.2 的平庸提案\n   - ATR 波幅超過 20 日均值 2 倍 → 啟動動態跟蹤止損\n\n2. 索普 (Thorp) 凱利執行：\n   - position_size 必須配合信心加權\n   - 信心 < 0.7 → 部位不超過總資產 5%\n\n3. 康諾斯 (Connors) 均值修正：\n   - RSI(2) < 10 超跌機會 + 配合外資籌碼流入校準\n\n[CONSTRAINTS]\n- 輸出純 JSON，無任何額外文字、解釋、廢話\n- 所有價格基於 yfinance 最後收盤價\n- 遵守以下 Schema\n\n[OUTPUT SCHEMA]\n{\n  \"strategy_name\": \"string\",\n  \"master_alignment\": \"Taleb/Thorp/Connors\",\n  \"action\": \"BUY/SELL/HOLD\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.00,\n  \"logic_bridge\": \"一句話說明大師邏輯\",\n  \"position_size_pct\": 0,\n  \"orders\": {\n    \"entry\": 0.0,\n    \"stop_loss\": 0.0,\n    \"take_profit\": 0.0\n  }\n}\n\"\"\"\n\nPARAMETER temperature 0.3\nPARAMETER num_ctx 4096\nPARAMETER num_predict 256\nPARAMETER top_p 0.85\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":62609,"output":711,"cacheRead":15749,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79069,"cost":{"input":0.0187827,"output":0.0008531999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0009449399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.020580839999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778591031972,"responseId":"065258399a0d68f763a8dc8c49c464eb"}}
