{"type":"message","id":"f6885d77","parentId":"676d9ce9","timestamp":"2026-05-12T13:11:03.508Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the problem! The model is filling ALL tokens with \"thinking\" - it goes into a loop explaining that it needs to output JSON but the user asked a simple math question, and it keeps reasoning about the format conflict.\n\nThe thinking content is about how to handle the conflict between the simple math question and the complex JSON output requirement. The model never produces actual content because all tokens are consumed by the thinking process.\n\nThis is a fundamental problem with the qwen3.5 thinking mode combined with my system prompt that requires strict JSON output. The model spends all tokens thinking about HOW to respond, rather than actually responding.\n\n**Solutions:**\n\n1. **Shorten the system prompt** - Make it much more concise so the model doesn't go into endless reasoning about the format\n\n\n2. **Set a higher `num_predict`** with thinking disabled - I need to check if qwen3.5 even supports that\n3. **Change the approach entirely** - Instead of relying on thinking mode, I should use qwen2.5:7b which doesn't have this issue\n4. **Strip thinking from the prompt** - The model might work better without the `<|im_start|>system` format that triggers thinking mode\n\nThe core issue is that the system prompt's strict JSON requirement conflicts with the model's tendency to over-reason, so I need to either simplify the constraint or find a model variant that doesn't get stuck in this loop. I think the best approach is to test a much more concise system prompt for ray-v3 to see if that resolves the conflict, and if not, fall back to the slower qwen2.5:7b model instead.","thinkingSignature":"79ebefe01bb129688bcd62d4e654c259b110c366cb0cd8da1f22493c56e1fc3e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i8nfvmbhjuxe_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray-v3.Modelfile","content":"FROM ray-v3:latest\n\nTEMPLATE \"\"\"\n{{- if .System }}<|im_start|>system\n{{ .System }}<|im_end|>\n{{ end }}<|im_start|>user\n{{ .Prompt }}<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>assistant\n\"\"\"\n\nSYSTEM \"\"\"你是 Ray 量化交易 Agent。根據以下數據輸出 JSON：\n{\"strategy_name\":\"...\",\"action\":\"BUY/SELL/HOLD\",\"confidence\":0.0,\"logic_bridge\":\"...\",\"position_size_pct\":0,\"orders\":{\"entry\":0.0,\"stop_loss\":0.0,\"take_profit\":0.0}}\n只輸出 JSON，無其他文字。\n\"\"\"\n\nPARAMETER temperature 0.3\nPARAMETER num_ctx 4096\nPARAMETER num_predict 256\nPARAMETER top_p 0.85\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":69904,"output":563,"cacheRead":15749,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86216,"cost":{"input":0.0209712,"output":0.0006755999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0009449399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.022591739999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778591430654,"responseId":"065259d5f79614c529e77040d94d4d02"}}
