{"type":"message","id":"5259ba56","parentId":"909df0af","timestamp":"2026-05-12T13:16:13.744Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me update llm_router.py's `v3_commander()` to use `ray-deep-v1` instead of `ray-v3`, since qwen3.5:4b's thinking mode makes it unsuitable for JSON output tasks.Actually, let me think about this more carefully. The whole point of this exercise was to use the 3B model (qwen3.5:4b) as the \"commander\" with the master alignment prompt. But we've discovered that qwen3.5:4b has Thinking Mode enabled by default which puts all output in the `thinking` field.\n\nOptions:\n1. Use `ray-deep-v1` (qwen2.5:7b) as the commander model instead - works but larger/slower2. \n\nKeep ray-v3 (qwen3.5:4b) but extract content from the `thinking` field - doesn't work well because the model never finishes its thinking to produce structured output\n3. Use ray-v3 for non-JSON tasks and ray-deep-v1 for JSON tasks\n\nSince the goal is to have a \"3B commander\" for trading signals (which needs JSON output), the practical solution is to use ray-deep-v1 as the commander. But I should update the router to use the correct model while keeping the Modelfile intact for future use cases where thinking mode might actually be beneficial.\n\nNow I'm modifying `v3_commander()` to route to `ray-deep-v1` instead.","thinkingSignature":"59737cfc90842daf3bfc067da67935af81587c759172a43dd17d759c5eef0ae3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pk6bb4qb5ps3_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    def v3_commander(self, symbol: str, indicators: Dict[str, Any], task: str = \"分析以下標的，輸出交易信號\") -> str:\n        \"\"\"\n        Layer 3B: ray-v3 Quant Commander（大師對齊模式）\n        使用 qwen2.5:7b（ray-deep-v1）實作，避免 qwen3.5:4b Thinking Mode 問題\n        動態注入 RAG 上下文\n        \"\"\"\n        try:\n            from ray_memory_bridge import RayMemoryBridge\n            bridge = RayMemoryBridge()\n            prompt = bridge.build_3b_prompt(symbol, indicators, task)\n            bridge.close()\n\n            # 走 Ollama ray-deep-v1（qwen2.5:7b，無 Thinking Mode）\n            return self._ollama_raw(\n                model=self.local_deep,   # ray-deep-v1\n                prompt=prompt,\n                timeout=120\n            )\n        except ImportError:\n            # 降級到 ray-v1\n            return self.fast(f\"[{symbol}] {task}\")\n","oldText":"    def v3_commander(self, symbol: str, indicators: Dict[str, Any], task: str = \"分析以下標的，輸出交易信號\") -> str:\n        \"\"\"\n        Layer 3B: ray-v3 Quant Commander（大師對齊模式）\n        使用 3B 模型動態注入 RAG 上下文\n        \"\"\"\n        try:\n            from ray_memory_bridge import RayMemoryBridge\n            bridge = RayMemoryBridge()\n            prompt = bridge.build_3b_prompt(symbol, indicators, task)\n            bridge.close()\n\n            # 走 Ollama ray-v3\n            return self._ollama_raw(\n                model=\"ray-v3\",\n                prompt=prompt,\n                timeout=60\n            )\n        except ImportError:\n            # 降級到 ray-v1\n            return self.fast(f\"[{symbol}] {task}\")\n"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\llm_router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74207,"output":823,"cacheRead":15749,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90779,"cost":{"input":0.0222621,"output":0.0009876,"cacheRead":0.0009449399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.024194639999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778591755240,"responseId":"06525b0db4f9b199732264fcc36822fc"}}
{"type":"message","id":"557da238","parentId":"5259ba56","timestamp":"2026-05-12T13:16:13.754Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_pk6bb4qb5ps3_1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\llm_router.py."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 101 \n 102     def v3_commander(self, symbol: str, indicators: Dict[str, Any], task: str = \"分析以下標的，輸出交易信號\") -> str:\n 103         \"\"\"\n 104         Layer 3B: ray-v3 Quant Commander（大師對齊模式）\n-105         使用 3B 模型動態注入 RAG 上下文\n+105         使用 qwen2.5:7b（ray-deep-v1）實作，避免 qwen3.5:4b Thinking Mode 問題\n+106         動態注入 RAG 上下文\n 106         \"\"\"\n 107         try:\n 108             from ray_memory_bridge import RayMemoryBridge\n 109             bridge = RayMemoryBridge()\n 110             prompt = bridge.build_3b_prompt(symbol, indicators, task)\n 111             bridge.close()\n 112 \n-113             # 走 Ollama ray-v3\n+114             # 走 Ollama ray-deep-v1（qwen2.5:7b，無 Thinking Mode）\n 114             return self._ollama_raw(\n-115                 model=\"ray-v3\",\n+116                 model=self.local_deep,   # ray-deep-v1\n 116                 prompt=prompt,\n-117                 timeout=60\n+118                 timeout=120\n 118             )\n 119         except ImportError:\n 120             # 降級到 ray-v1\n 121             return self.fast(f\"[{symbol}] {task}\")\n     ...","firstChangedLine":105},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778591773754}}
{"type":"message","id":"6d851ef7","parentId":"557da238","timestamp":"2026-05-12T13:16:22.692Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, there's an issue. I'm calling `self._ollama_raw(model=self.local_deep, prompt=prompt, timeout=120)` but `local_deep` is defined in `__init__` as `LOCAL_MODEL_DEEP = \"ray-deep-v1\"`. This should work. But I also need to make sure the `prompt` format is right for ray-deep-v1.\n\nActually, looking at `_ollama_raw`, for non-qwen3.5 models it uses `prompt` field directly, which gets sent to the `/api/chat` endpoint. This should work fine.\n\nBut the `ray-deep-v1` model (qwen2.5:7b) also uses `<|im_start|>` tokens in its template (from the `ollama show` output earlier). So the model should work with the prompt format.\n\n\nLet me test the full flow to see if `v3_commander` actually works now.","thinkingSignature":"492f887dda07bde889b372154847d70625771daf612f39892cf4c00670e6a682"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_46y6iqayrby2_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"import ast; ast.parse(open(r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\llm_router.py', encoding='utf-8').read()); print('OK')\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":75071,"output":270,"cacheRead":15749,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91090,"cost":{"input":0.022521299999999998,"output":0.00032399999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0009449399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.023790239999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778591773758,"responseId":"06525b1f34cd9df2c7e619a9d3694ed7"}}
