{"type":"message","id":"66bafbfb","parentId":"631de96f","timestamp":"2026-05-12T13:25:26.507Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_1qbmu05sdl0e_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== Test: ray-v3 Quant Commander ===\r\n\r\n1. Test ray_memory_bridge.build_3b_prompt()\r\n   Prompt length: 704 chars\r\n   Prompt preview:\r\n### 市場數據\r\n標的：VOO\r\n現價：478.5\r\nRSI：42.3\r\nK線：478.50 (+1.2%)\r\n\r\n\r\n### 動態上下文（RAG）\r\n【本地歷史教訓】\r\n- [0.85] [TALEB] Fat-tail risk warning: current market volatility underestimated\r\n- [0.75] 當Sharpe比率低于0.5時，表明投資回報相對於風險過低。\r\n- [0.75] RSI指標在65至35之間時，表明市場處於超買或超賣狀態。\r\n- [0.75] 當Sharpe比率低于0.5時，表明投資回報與風險不匹配。\r\n- [0.75] RSI指數在60以上且價格創\r\n   [OK] build_3b_prompt\r\n\r\n2. Test llm_router.v3_commander()\r\n   Time: 27.1s\r\n   Result preview: ```json\r\n{\r\n    \"diagnosis\": \"当前VOO的RSI值为42.3，在65至35之间，表明市场处于超卖状态。然而，价格并未创新高，且近期涨幅较小（+1.2%），这可能意味着趋势尚未明显转向。\",\r\n    \"corrected_axiom\": {\r\n        \"original_axiom\": \"[0.75] RSI指數在60以上且價格創新高時，可能預示著趨勢轉折點。\",\r\n \r\n   [OK] v3_commander\r\n\r\n3. Test ray_brain.v3_commander_propose()\r\n   Indicators: RSI=2.61, price=679.52\r\n   Signal: N/A, conf=0.9\r\n   Full: {\"diagnosis\": \"当前市场存在尾部风险预警，VOO的市场价格创新高但未见RSI指标验证，表明可能处于超买状态。Sharpe比率低于0.5进一步确认投资回报与风险不匹配。\", \"corrected_axiom\": {\"axiom\": \"当Sharpe比率低于0.5且价格创新高而RSI未显示超卖时，应视为潜在的卖出信号。\", \"confidence\": 0.8, \"master_refer\r\n   [OK] v3_commander_propose\r\n\r\n=== Done ==="}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":52882,"aggregated":"=== Test: ray-v3 Quant Commander ===\r\n\r\n1. Test ray_memory_bridge.build_3b_prompt()\r\n   Prompt length: 704 chars\r\n   Prompt preview:\r\n### 市場數據\r\n標的：VOO\r\n現價：478.5\r\nRSI：42.3\r\nK線：478.50 (+1.2%)\r\n\r\n\r\n### 動態上下文（RAG）\r\n【本地歷史教訓】\r\n- [0.85] [TALEB] Fat-tail risk warning: current market volatility underestimated\r\n- [0.75] 當Sharpe比率低于0.5時，表明投資回報相對於風險過低。\r\n- [0.75] RSI指標在65至35之間時，表明市場處於超買或超賣狀態。\r\n- [0.75] 當Sharpe比率低于0.5時，表明投資回報與風險不匹配。\r\n