{"type":"message","id":"f27fe5fc","parentId":"2b1b76f1","timestamp":"2026-05-12T13:26:52.628Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_citzxlxb3wxa_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== Test: ray-v3 Quant Commander ===\r\n\r\n1. Test ray_memory_bridge.build_3b_prompt()\r\n   Prompt length: 704 chars\r\n   Prompt preview:\r\n### 市場數據\r\n標的：VOO\r\n現價：478.5\r\nRSI：42.3\r\nK線：478.50 (+1.2%)\r\n\r\n\r\n### 動態上下文（RAG）\r\n【本地歷史教訓】\r\n- [0.85] [TALEB] Fat-tail risk warning: current market volatility underestimated\r\n- [0.75] 當Sharpe比率低于0.5時，表明投資回報相對於風險過低。\r\n- [0.75] RSI指標在65至35之間時，表明市場處於超買或超賣狀態。\r\n- [0.75] 當Sharpe比率低于0.5時，表明投資回報與風險不匹配。\r\n- [0.75] RSI指數在60以上且價格創\r\n   [OK] build_3b_prompt\r\n\r\n2. Test llm_router.v3_commander()\r\n   Time: 21.4s\r\n   Result preview: ```json\r\n{\r\n  \"strategy_name\": \"RAY-V3 QUANT COMMANDER\",\r\n  \"master_alignment\": \"Taleb\",\r\n  \"action\": \"HOLD\",\r\n  \"confidence\": 0.85,\r\n  \"logic_bridge\": \"根據塔雷伯的肥尾風險警告，當前市場波動被低估，且Sharpe比率低于0.5，表明投資回報相對於風險過低。\"\r\n   [OK] v3_commander\r\n\r\n3. Test ray_brain.v3_commander_propose()\r\n   Indicators: RSI=2.61, price=679.52\r\n   Signal: SELL, conf=0.85\r\n   Full: {\"strategy_name\": \"RAY_V3_QUANT_COMMANDER\", \"master_alignment\": \"Taleb\", \"action\": \"SELL\", \"confidence\": 0.85, \"logic_bridge\": \"根據塔雷伯的肥尾風險警告，當前市場波動性被低估，且Sharpe比率低于0.5，表明投資回報相對於風險過低。\", \"position_size_p\r\n   [OK] v3_commander_propose\r\n\r\n=== Done ==="}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":44562,"aggregated":"=== Test: ray-v3 Quant Commander ===\r\n\r\n1. Test ray_memory_bridge.build_3b_prompt()\r\n   Prompt length: 704 chars\r\n   Prompt preview:\r\n### 市場數據\r\n標的：VOO\r\n現價：478.5\r\nRSI：42.3\r\nK線：478.50 (+1.2%)\r\n\r\n\r\n### 動態上下文（RAG）\r\n【本地歷史教訓】\r\n- [0.85] [TALEB] Fat-tail risk warning: current market volatility underestimated\r\n- [0.75] 當Sharpe比率低于0.5時，表明投資回報相對於風險過低。\r\n- [0.75] RSI指標在65至35之間時，表明市場處於超買或超賣狀態。\r\n- [0.75] 當Sharpe比率低于0.5