{"type":"message","id":"49389174","parentId":"c15e0218","timestamp":"2026-05-12T13:30:26.397Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Jo sent the same request again (the 3B Master Alignment Prompt). Looking at the previous conversation, I already implemented the entire system successfully! Let me check what was accomplished:\n\n1. ✅ ray-v3.Modelfile created (discovered qwen3.5:4b has Thinking Mode issue)\n2. ✅ ray-commander.Modelfile created (qwen2.5:7b + Master Alignment)\n3. ✅ ray_memory_bridge.build_3b_prompt() upgraded\n4. ✅ llm_router.v3_commander() implemented\n5. ✅ ray_brain.v3_commander_propose() implemented\n\n\n6. ✅ Test passed: action=HOLD, confidence=0.85, logic_bridge=Taler\n\nThe system is fully working now, so Jo must be resending the original message—likely due to Telegram's retry mechanism or a re-delivery. I should acknowledge this and confirm the implementation is already complete.","thinkingSignature":"f6d19af1272029a148cb9a8c6266cc8687987724859254df5d115c7756cd000d"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]\n\n這套系統已經在上一輪實作完成了 ✅ 直接給你最終確認：\n\n---\n\n## 📦 已實作完畢（2026-05-12 20:46）\n\n### 架構成果\n\n| 組件 | 狀態 | 備註 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `ray-v3.Modelfile` | ✅ 已建立 | qwen3.5:4b Thinking Mode 特性已記錄 |\n| `ray-commander.Modelfile` | ✅ 已建立 | qwen2.5:7b + 大師對齊 System Prompt |\n| `ray_memory_bridge.build_3b_prompt()` | ✅ 已升級 | 注入 RAG_CONTEXT（歷史教訓 + Taleb/Thorp 動態）|\n| `llm_router.v3_commander()` | ✅ 已實作 | 動態調度 ray-commander |\n| `ray_brain.v3_commander_propose()` | ✅ 已整合 | 直接吃 local_indicators |\n\n### 實測結果\n\n```\naction: HOLD\nconfidence: 0.85\nlogic_bridge: \"根據塔雷伯的肥尾風險警告...\"\nstrategy_name: RAY_V3_QUANT_COMMANDER\n```\n\n### ⚠️ 重要發現：qwen3.5:4b Thinking Mode\n\nqwen3.5:4b 內建 Thinking Mode，**所有輸出一律進 `thinking` 欄位**，導致 `content` 永遠為空。`eval_count: 256` 全部消耗在推理過程，JSON 永遠出不來。\n\n**對策：主力模型改用 `ray-commander`（qwen2.5:7b）。**\n\n---\n\n### 下一步（建議）\n\n1. **P1**：將 `us_scan_live.py` 的交易雷達接入 `v3_commander_propose`\n2. **P2**：建設 Ra